# Pomona

Read **AGENTS.md** at repo root before coding.

- Phase 2 next: dashboard + SQLite in `services/core/`
- Platform repo only — ML training is `pomona-agronomist-llm` (sibling)
- Every service: `/health`, JSON API, FastAPI + Pydantic
- LLM must NOT control actuators directly
- Run `make test` after changes; update `docs/PROJECT_STATUS.md` on milestones
- Personal notes: `private/` (gitignored) — never commit `.env` or weights

Quick commands: `./scripts/up.sh`, `./scripts/sim.sh`, `make test`

Install: [docs/INSTALL.md](docs/INSTALL.md) — Docker (all OS) or pip dev
